name: imaginary islands of distant lands map 2/5
description: The second map of my series of the imaginary islands of distant lands. Illustrating only at night for a few of weeks, this highly detailed map grew slowly out of nothing but wandering through a mind full of anxiety and onto my ipad. Each of these series takes place at golden hour, drawing highlights and long shadows emphasizing the unique terrain of these unexplored lands. (copyright)@davekiehl for personal use only.
